&lt;text&gt;The Message with special character &#039;$&#039; will be replaced by finding value in eventPayLoad from CurveTable(&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;text tag=&quot;NoSpace&quot; eventPayLoad=&quot;Default.HorizonUIDemoAttributeSet.Health, 1.4&quot;&gt;$&lt;/text&gt;
